name: Signs
overview: When a young woman's murder shows similarities to a decade-old cold case, a new police commander must break the silence permeating an Owl Mountain town.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Trela, the gruff new police chief of a small mountain village, is immediately put to the test when the friend of a fellow police officer disappears.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: A grisly find inspires memories of a similar unsolved murder. Trela brings Błażej in for questioning. Ada learns a shocking truth.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Trela crosses paths with the previous police chief. A gruesome discovery is kept under wraps. Ada questions Targosz about Patrycja's death.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Armed with new information, Trela and Ada re-examine Laura's murder from ten years ago. Jonasz snoops through Ms. Bławatska's documents.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Kasia's mission to hide money from her father is interrupted. Trela and Ada track down and talk to Robert. Nina shares a secret with Agata.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Another murder victim turns up in the village, Agata lays a cunning trap, Błażej suffers a setback and Radek finds a wealthy buyer.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A new investigator takes over for Trela, who refuses to stop searching for answers. Meanwhile, Radek lawyers up and Targosz and Paszke feel the heat.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: The village's dark and painful past finally comes to light as residents struggle to accept their shared history.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Trela's grief over Nina's disappearance drives him to dangerous habits. Meanwhile, the mayoral race heats up, while Ksiądz follows his intuition.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Nina returns home, unable to speak about her ordeal. Police investigate Bławatska's story. Błażej's campaign proves formidable.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Ada grows increasingly concerned about Sobczyk. Also, Agata learns a painful lesson and Błażej starts to have second thoughts about politics.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: With Agata missing, the mayor pleads with both Trela and Jonasz for assistance. Błażej takes a big step. Ada makes a shocking discovery.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Police recover Kasia's missing bicycle. Meanwhile, Agata's problems go from bad to worse and Jonasz pays the mayor a visit.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Tragedy strikes, leading some to wonder if the village is cursed. The mayoral debate takes an unexpected turn. Błażej tries to reconnect with Ada.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Trela closes in on the truth behind the missing family. Ada comes to an uncomfortable conclusion. Nina confronts Dorotka. Błażej loses control.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: As Election Day arrives, police dig for answers into the hit-and-run death. Also, Twerski and Kaja set a diversion then hunt for treasure.
